recounts  an event which occurred up to two rounds previous which  he  viewed
firsthand. The wizard, while recounting the incident, modifies it in the  way
which  he  would have liked for it to occur. At the end of the  casting,  the
past  will  be  rewoven along the lines of the wizard's version,  by  a  base
guideline of 3% per level of the wizard.
