be  recovered  at a rate of 1 HP per round of rest or 1 HP per turn  of  mild
activity, but not at all for strenuous activity. Creatures brought below zero
hit  point  because of this illusionary damage will be unconscious  and  must
make a system shock survival roll of else die of shock, losing 1 HP per round
until  reaching -10, unless they receive aid. Even creatures that can be  hit
by  only  by silver, iron or magical weapons will suffer from all  the  above
effects unless they have some special resistance to illusions (or have reason
to be suspicious and disbelieve).
