critical wounds to any normal plant or animal it touches, once per round.
           5. Olympus. This weapon is made of fine, polished steel. It cannot
strike  chaotic  good  creatures,  but does  double  damage  to  lawful  evil
creatures.  It  can create food and wine upon command, as  the  priest  spell
