     01-60. Elemental plane. Roll 1d4 to determine which:
           1.  Air. This plume manifests as a titanic surge of swirling wind,
much like an upended tornado. Its force is directed upward, however, and does
not  trap creatures. Creatures making a saving throw versus breath weapon are
thrown  3  yards horizontally for 3d6 damage; those failing are  hurled  high
