damage  (half  if a creature saves) and creatures failing their saving  throw
fall  off  the column (taking appropriate falling damage in all probability).
It does double damage to gaseous or aerial creatures, but these are of course
not subject to falling damage. The stone summoned is relatively permanent.
           3.  Fire. This plume is a tremendously hot column of roaring fire.
It does 8d8 flame damage to all within its area (save for half damage). Those
