creatures,  but does double damage to creatures with a link to  the  positive
material plane.
          2. Positive material plane. The weapon causes its special damage as
healing  to any living being, but if the being is already at full hit points,
this  applies  as "damage". This "damage" is actual, but does  not  count  as
pulling a creature below full hit points in terms of this spell. On a natural
19  or  20, it acts as a mace of disruption versus undead. Undead take double
