           6. Gladsheim. This weapon crackles with lightning and fire, and is
made  of  fine  steel.  It  cannot strike chaotic good  and  chaotic  neutral
creatures,  but  does  double  damage  to  lawful  neutral  and  lawful  evil
creatures. It gives a +4 to-hit and -4 on AC to any chaotic good and  chaotic
neutral warrior within 4 yards.
           7-9.  Limbo. This weapon randomly shifts colour, composition,  and
radiance  every  round. It can strike any creature  who  can  be  hit  by  +4
weapons. Any spell effect directed at the wielder changes into a wild  surge.
