flaming,  or by the indicated saving throws. If extinguished by reduction  in
temperature to -5 C (+23 F), or by magical means which end flame or heat, the
paste  will lie dormant until it heats up or is given oxygen. Then the  paste
will continue to burn for the remainder of the spell's duration.
