initiative. Also, the weavers cannot be separated by more than 10  feet,  and
no  barriers may be between any individual and the head caster. The number of
mages involved is also limited: 7 for a major weaving. Minor weavers count as
when  included in a major weaving for the purpose of calculating the  maximum
number of mages. A major weaver counts as   if included in a master weaving.
