will be branded insane or bewitched, and treated appropriately. NPCs who  are
subjected  to  this  spell will spend at least the next  day  sulking,  still
afraid of everyone (this is not a magical effect, simply an after-effect). If
an  NPC  knows who cast the spell, they will either be afraid of  the  wizard
(for weaker NPCs) or very angry (stronger NPCs).
