will behave in a feminine rather than an effeminate manner, and similarly for
females;  the subject has no desire to parody. If the subject's  species  has
more  than  two genders, the resulting gender orientation is DM's choice.  If
the  species  has  only one gender, the subject is unaffected.  The  material
component of this spell is a piece of wood with a yin-and-yang symbol  carved
upon it.
