plane of shadow. This process permanently incurs a psychological weakness  in
the  caster,  amplifying  some  trait which  formerly  existed  into  a  true
downfall.  This may not actually cause the shade to be incapable of happiness
or  meaningful existence, but it does add an element of the tragic into their
nature.
