conjure  spell expires). The priest must begin the conjuring spell the  round
immediately  after  casting  this  spell. Should  he  fail  to  initiate  the
conjuring  during  the  following round, or should he fail  to  complete  the
conjuring (because he takes damage, for example) this spell is wasted.
