successful,  overcomes  the  priest's control and  becomes  free-willed.  The
material  component of this spell is a black opal of 100 or more gold  pieces
value.
Duplicated from Dungeon Magazine #35, page 56:

     Ether Shadow

     Climate/Terrain: Any ruins or subterranean chambers
     Frequency: Very rare
     Organization: Solitary
     Activity cycle: Night or darkness
     Diet: Living beings
     Intelligence: Highly
